Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_design_settop(25.10)                            init_design_settop(25.10)

Name
       init_design_settop

Syntax
       init_design_settop <value>

       Type: Integer

       Default: 1

       Specifies whether the top cell name is automatically assigned (0) or is
       set by the user (1). This global variable replaces the previous rda_In-
       put(ui_settop) configuration file variable.

Example
              * The  following command specifies that the top cell name is as-
                signed automatically.

                set init_design_settop {0}

Related Information
              * init_design

